                      "content": "Today was tough, but you did something important — you agreed to look at how you operate. I noticed how quickly you switch topics when things get scary. And how a simple unlocked door becomes a whole story about not being cared for. This isn’t your fault — it’s your way of protecting yourself from fear of rejection.",
